00:32:28.918 --> 00:32:31.758
It's, people might think,
oh that's a terrible thing.

00:32:31.968 --> 00:32:36.308
But none of it is it's all knowledge and
knowledge is a gift, until you can name

00:32:36.308 --> 00:32:38.888
a thing and then fully recognizing it.

00:32:38.888 --> 00:32:41.678
And that's actually the hard
part for full recognition.

00:32:41.888 --> 00:32:42.908
Naming is easy.

00:32:43.328 --> 00:32:47.378
Full recognition of what it means is
difficult, but unless you do that, you

00:32:47.378 --> 00:32:49.173
can't actually use what you've got.

00:32:49.673 --> 00:32:53.638
<v Dr Pam>That brings to mind something
