00:32:53.758 --> 00:33:00.568
often wondered about myself is naming
something, I hear what you're saying,

00:33:00.598 --> 00:33:04.238
but there's more, people say okay,
if you've got those things, you've

00:33:04.238 --> 00:33:07.598
still got them, whether you name them
or not, what good does it do you?

00:33:07.988 --> 00:33:11.358
But I think what I'm hearing you
say is, it does you good, because

00:33:11.358 --> 00:33:15.738
then with self knowledge, you can
work your way through or around

00:33:15.738 --> 00:33:18.168
those things to have a better life.

00:33:18.768 --> 00:33:19.308
<v Kylee>Yes.

00:33:19.308 --> 00:33:22.158
I think through is the only
way, around is avoidance.

00:33:22.578 --> 00:33:27.108
And that's something I learned rec only
recently because people used to ask me,

00:33:28.198 --> 00:33:30.028
don't you ever think of what you lost?

00:33:30.118 --> 00:33:33.268
Because I used to talk about
my burnout as a nervous break.

00:33:33.298 --> 00:33:36.448
I suppose it was a breakdown, but it
really was autistic burnout, I think.

00:33:37.108 --> 00:33:38.818
I think it's probably what it was.

00:33:39.368 --> 00:33:43.178
And I used to say no, there's
no point in going there, which

00:33:43.178 --> 00:33:44.498
is actually what was wrong.

00:33:44.498 --> 00:33:50.708
Because what I would have done if
I had known better was yes, it's

00:33:50.708 --> 00:33:54.938
important to recognize it fully because
you can't process it until you do.

00:33:55.688 --> 00:33:57.698
So avoiding, you can't work around it.

